==Hindi==
===Pronunciation===
/ je: / though rarely also / jəhə /

===Demonstrative pronoun===
'''यह''' (yaha)

# [[this]] - direct case only, see below for oblique. (Plural: [[ये]])
#:Example: "यह मकान बड़ा है" - This house is large
# [[he]] - direct case only. (If [[respect]] is conveyed, ये is used)
#:Example: "यह छोटा है" - He is small
# [[she]] - direct case only. (If [[respect]] is conveyed, ये is used)
#:Example "यह छोटी है" - She is small
# [[it]] - direct case only.

====Inflection====
[[Oblique]]: [[इस]]

